Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Press freedom
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bxnt
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Apr 1979
Press freedom challenged as CBS 'Sixty Minutes' programme is sued for libel. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.